'''Danilo Larangeira''', known as '''Danilo''' (born May 10, 1984), is a Brazilian [[Association football|football]] [[Centre back|central defender]], who currently plays for [[Udinese Calcio|Udinese]] and is considered one of the best defenders in the Serie A.

==Career==

On December 16, 2009 [[Sociedade Esportiva Palmeiras|Palmeiras]] have made official the ransom from [[Clube Atl<U+00E9>tico Paranaense|Atl<U+00E9>tico Paranaense]] of the central defender, first market trade of Verd<U+00E3>o for the 2010 season, the footballer arrived on loan at the beginning of 2009. Verd<U+00E3>o partnered with [[Traffic Group]] to sign him<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www2.cbf.com.br/php/bid.php?d=14/01/2010&uf=%3F|title=Boletim Informativo Di<U+00E1>rio Eletr<U+00F4>nico (BID-E) Rela<U+00E7><U+00E3>o Pela Data 14/01/2010|date=January 14, 2010|accessdate=May 31, 2011|work=CBF|language=Portuguese|archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5z5dQgzP4|archivedate=May 31, 2011}}</ref> and Atl<U+00E9>tico Paranaense retained 20% rights.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dgabc.com.br/News/5784027/danilo-fica-no-palmeiras.aspx|title=Danilo fica no Palmeiras|date=December 16, 2009|accessdate=May 31, 2011|work=Di<U+00E1>rio do Grande ABC|language=Portuguese}}</ref>

In April 2010 he gained national attention when he was accused of [[racism]] by [[Clube Atl<U+00E9>tico Paranaense]]'s defender [[Manoel Messias Silva Carvalho|Manoel]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://esporte.uol.com.br/futebol/campeonatos/copa-do-brasil/ultimas-noticias/2010/04/17/zagueiro-manoel-volta-a-falar-e-diz-que-ficou-transtornado-com-episodio.jhtm|title=Zagueiro Manoel volta a falar e diz que ficou "transtornado" com epis<U+00F3>dio|date=April 17, 2010|publisher=[[Universo Online|UOL Esportes]]|language=Portuguese|accessdate=April 17, 2010}}</ref> During a match between Atl<U+00E9>tico and Palmeiras on April 15, TV cameras captured a scene in which Danilo called Manoel "macaco" (monkey in Portuguese language). Danilo later publicly admitted that he offended and spat Manoel, which reported the incident to a police station in S<U+00E3>o Paulo just after the match.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.simplyfutbol.com/2010/04/palmeiras-defender-danilo-could-face.html|title=Palmeiras defender Danilo could face jail time|last=Lugo|first=Lucas|date=April 17, 2010|publisher=Simply F<U+00FA>tbol|accessdate=April 17, 2010}} {{Dead link|date=October 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref> In January 2013, the S<U+00E3>o Paulo Criminal Court sentenced him to one year in prison, although he is expected to have the punishment reduced to a fine on appeal.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.football-italia.net/29272/danilo-guilty-racist-abuse |title=Danilo guilty of racist abuse |publisher=Football Italia |date=January 9, 2013 |accessdate=September 5, 2013}}</ref> On September 4, 2013, Larangeira signed a two-year extension keeping him at the club until 2018.{{Citation needed|date=September 2013}}

